eping up on their target and only do so if he sees Heyward in danger. Hawkeye also changes his mind about using his weapon when he realizes the 'savage' is unaware of their presence. This cautious behavior suggests that they are aware of potential dangers and are taking measures to avoid detection while maintaining the ability to defend themselves if necessary.">
